trans-unit.source: Manages a collection of user-interface related <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Glyph"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Behandler en samling av brukergrensesnittet relatert <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Glyph"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: Each Adorner can be enabled and disabled.
trans-unit.target: Hver Adorner kan aktivert og deaktivert.

trans-unit.source: Only enabled Adorner objects will receive hit test and paint messages from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>.
trans-unit.target: Bare aktivert Adorner objekter får treffprosent test og paint meldinger fra <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>

trans-unit.source: An Adorner can be viewed as a proxy between user-interface related elements, which consist of all <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Glyph> objects, and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>.
trans-unit.target: En Adorner kan vises som en proxy mellom brukergrensesnittet relaterte elementer som består av alle <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Glyph>objekter, og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Glyph>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Behavior Service Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [virkemåte tjenesteoversikt](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The Adorner constructor creates a new <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.GlyphCollection> and is enabled, by default.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren Adorner oppretter en ny <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.GlyphCollection>og er aktivert som standard.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.GlyphCollection>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService"></xref> associated with the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService"> </xref> knyttet til den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When an <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner> is added to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorServiceAdornerCollection> of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>, the collection sets this property so that the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner> can call back to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>.
trans-unit.target: Når en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner>legges til i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorServiceAdornerCollection>av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>, samlingen, settes denne egenskapen slik at <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner>kan ringe tilbake til <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorServiceAdornerCollection> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating if the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner"></xref> is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir hvis den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner"> </xref> er aktivert.

trans-unit.source: If the Enabled property is `true`, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService> class will send `HitTest` and `Paint` messages to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis egenskapen Enabled `true`, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>klassen sender `HitTest` og `Paint` meldinger til <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.Adorner> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorService>
